    Author:

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      Object getSummary()
      Implementations are encouraged to return an inline created new Object() whose toString() method will return the actual String instead of just returning the String directly.

    • Method Detail

      • getSummary

        Object getSummary()
        Implementations are encouraged to return an inline created new Object() whose toString() method will return the actual String instead of just returning the String directly. This helps loggers be more efficient as the String won't be generated until the log level demands it.
        Returns:
        An object whose toString method will return a summary of this object.
